OL,7,FCharities have backed an urgent
OL,8,Fexpansion in routine HIV testing in
OL,9,Fhospitals, after promising results
OL,10,Ffrom an NHS England trial that
OL,11,Fdiagnosed hundreds of undetected
OL,12,Fcases.
OL,14,FThe pilot, which has been running
OL,15,Fsince April 2022 in 33 hospital
OL,16,Femergency departments across London,
OL,17,FBrighton, Manchester and Blackpool,
OL,18,Fsees patients tested for HIV as well
OL,19,Fas Hepatitis B and C as part of
OL,20,Froutine blood tests.
OL,3,CRoutine HIV testing in hospitals
OL,4,C'must be expanded' as trial finds
OL,5,Chundreds living with virus
